{"tid":2017427,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】新一波本地疫情視乎「關鍵7日」 若梨木樹群組從事高危工作或增播毒風險","createTime":"2020-05-15T05:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T06:19:53.000Z","uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdefecd3571479cf25f57726a7027592b3aa770","tid":2017427,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎疫情有反覆迹象，荃灣梨木樹邨本地感染家庭群組最少3人確診，至今源頭未明。醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超表示，本港會否因而引起另一波本地染疫個案，<span style=\"color: red;\">未來7日是關鍵</span>，若未來7日社區沒有該家庭以外的個案，則之後再有個案的風險降低，但該9人家庭有8人有病徵，擔心之後會有其他家人確診，「家庭群組爆發唔止咁少人」，若有確診者從事高危工作或活動，或增加病毒擴散風險。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家呢幾日唔好出街</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feda15349fbdbc4fda1e41cf47fbdef895fcdbd","tid":2017427,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:00:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極危險</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁子超表示，是源頭個案機會較大。他同意以目前資料分析，是次家庭群組源頭病人是63歲男子機會較大，因他長時間在街邊擺檔，接觸到病毒及隱形病人機會較大。<br />\n<br />\n他指，本港會否因今次家庭群組而產生新一波本地感染個案，視乎病人於病毒傳染期間，體內病毒量及在社區的活動。<br />\n<br />\n該家庭9人中只有爺爺人沒病徵，而且嫲嫲病毒量較高，梁子超指，「<span style=\"color: red;\">擔心遲啲其他家人會陰轉陽，家庭群組爆發唔止咁少人</span>」，若有其他確診者從事高危工作，或有高危活動，例如會到酒吧，病毒傳播出社區風險將大增。<br />\n<br />\n梁子超續指，<span style=\"color: red;\">未來7日是關鍵</span>，「雖然病毒潛伏期可以係14日，甚至更長，但如果頭7日見唔到大型爆發，之後相對機會較少。如果頭7日已有個案，之後7日風險高好多」。"},{"pid":"e7e52e4e39560ba87a36c74f23324299d2bac8f3","tid":2017427,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家記住唔好出街<br />\n<br />\n勤力洗手同戴口罩</span>"},{"pid":"776fc1b57e5db82d772d776d375991e936c173dc","tid":2017427,"uid":155137,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"有銅心口罩 不怕"},{"pid":"2001bffab996e60d4d662a7a664f846c016bebc9","tid":2017427,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"776fc1b57e5db82d772d776d375991e936c173dc","tid":2017427,"uid":155137,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"有銅心口罩 不怕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">袁國勇：料800新冠肺炎隱形帶菌者社區播毒</span>"},{"pid":"3994e9490cfe70c1559f438fb3888d6289ffc014","tid":2017427,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:04:43.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情在全球擴散，香港大學微生物學系傳染病學講座教授袁國勇接受內地傳媒訪問時表示，許多新冠肺炎患者病症輕微，並以鑽石公主號郵輪回港的225人為例，<span style=\"color: orange;\">當中9人確診，但只有1人在檢測前有明顯病徵。他推算，若香港有100名患者被發現，可能有800名沒有病徵的感染者</span>，但他們已將病毒傳播，認同這次疫情的傳播鏈很難找得清楚。"},{"pid":"c1de4788cf7c0aa014e29097f96e3e1a856ace11","tid":2017427,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"776fc1b57e5db82d772d776d375991e936c173dc","tid":2017427,"uid":155137,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"有銅心口罩 不怕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"記住洗手，戴口罩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd2b44bbc884604a87f1659ef48089eff2c992a","tid":2017427,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}